      <title>刚果因成本飙升取消 12 亿美元身份识别系统合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/congo-cancels-1-2-billion-id-system-contract-after-costs-spiral</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数月前，政府监管机构警告称，刚果民主共和国取消了一项耗资 12 亿美元建立国家生物识别系统的项目，该项目存在成本超支和资金违规问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/congo-cancels-1-2-billion-id-system-contract-after-costs-spiral</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:46:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登自冻结许可以来首次批准新的液化天然气项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/biden-grants-first-new-lng-approval-since-freezing-permits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国能源部对联邦法院推翻临时禁令的裁决提出上诉，但拜登政府仍发放了自美国能源部今年 1 月暂停液化天然气出口许可以来的首个液化天然气出口许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/biden-grants-first-new-lng-approval-since-freezing-permits</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>柴油价格上涨导致哥伦比亚首都卡车司机陷入瘫痪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/truck-drivers-paralyze-colombia-s-capital-after-diesel-price-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡车司机封锁了通往波哥大的一些主要道路，抗议哥伦比亚近五年来首次提高柴油价格，导致学校停课，工人被困在交通堵塞中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/truck-drivers-paralyze-colombia-s-capital-after-diesel-price-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:31:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普面临是否可以停止封口费判决的裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/trump-faces-rulings-on-whether-he-can-stop-hush-money-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在纽约封口费案中面临一系列关键裁决，这些裁决将决定他是否会在 11 月总统大选之前被判刑，而检察官们正在反击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/trump-faces-rulings-on-whether-he-can-stop-hush-money-sentencing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯或特朗普领导下的外交政策可能会是什么样子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/podcast-what-foreign-policy-under-harris-or-trump-might-look-like</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前贸易代表迈克尔·弗罗曼 (Michael Froman) 讨论了世界对卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 或唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的期望，以及哈里斯如何与乔·拜登 (Joe Biden) 分道扬镳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/podcast-what-foreign-policy-under-harris-or-trump-might-look-like</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:11:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌干达反对党称领导人博比·瓦因受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/uganda-s-main-opposition-party-says-leader-bobi-wine-shot-in-leg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌干达主要反对党民族团结纲领党表示，该党领导人罗伯特·基亚古拉尼周二在首都坎帕拉郊区与警方的冲突中腿部中弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/uganda-s-main-opposition-party-says-leader-bobi-wine-shot-in-leg</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:04:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙推迟选择总理，缩短调整预算的时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/french-economy-latest-macron-s-pm-pick-delay-cuts-time-to-tweak-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国国民议会财政委员会主席表示，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙对任命谁为法国新总理进行了长时间的审议，这限制了议员们对预算做出重大修改的时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/french-economy-latest-macron-s-pm-pick-delay-cuts-time-to-tweak-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 16:25:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国股市上涨后将减持德国商业银行股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/german-government-plans-to-cut-its-stake-in-commerzbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府计划削减其在德国商业银行的股份，以抓住最近的股价上涨机会，退出这家十多年前被其救助的银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/german-government-plans-to-cut-its-stake-in-commerzbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 16:09:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥议员在体育中心开会以躲避抗议者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/protesters-block-off-mexican-congress-ahead-of-judicial-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[示威者在墨西哥下议院周围形成人链，迫使议员们转移到体育中心，抗议总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔的司法改革法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/protesters-block-off-mexican-congress-ahead-of-judicial-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:48:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管人质事件引发抗议，内塔尼亚胡仍坚持战争立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/israel-hamas-war-netanyahu-refuses-to-budge-despite-protests-over-hostages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对因哈马斯杀害六名人质和暂停部分英国武器销售许可证而引发的国内大规模抗议，以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡坚持对哈马斯采取强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/israel-hamas-war-netanyahu-refuses-to-budge-despite-protests-over-hostages</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 12:47:28 GMT</pubDate>
